  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/1569e00c25b6f2b6d033800f0a07519f.poster.avif?t=1774500989\" width=800 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/1569e00c25b6f2b6d033800f0a07519f.webm?t=1774500989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/1569e00c25b6f2b6d033800f0a07519f.mp4?t=1774500989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to <strong>HEXAROMA</strong>, the charming world of our island village builder! Dive into a relaxing yet challenging experience where puzzle and strategy meet city building. Set across beautiful hexagonal maps, this game lets you craft quaint villages amidst varied landscapes like snowy tundras, scorching deserts, lush steppes, towering mountains, and dense forests. As my first game, I am incredibly excited to share this cozy adventure with you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/1d4ad0625104285b5e42ca52f5ee3c46.poster.avif?t=1774500989\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/1d4ad0625104285b5e42ca52f5ee3c46.webm?t=1774500989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/1d4ad0625104285b5e42ca52f5ee3c46.mp4?t=1774500989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Why should you play this game? </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you're looking for a soothing yet engaging pastime, this is the perfect game for you. It’s designed to be a chill and wholesome escape, allowing you to unwind as you create adorable island communities. Whether you're a seasoned gamer or just looking for a relaxing way to pass the time, the delightful atmosphere and simple mechanics make it easy to pick up and enjoy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/c68c4e58ed33649be325b32b76e917d7.poster.avif?t=1774500989\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/c68c4e58ed33649be325b32b76e917d7.webm?t=1774500989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/c68c4e58ed33649be325b32b76e917d7.mp4?t=1774500989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay is straightforward but rewarding. Place buildings strategically to maximize your score—some structures thrive when close to others, while some need space to flourish. With each milestone you reach on the progress bar, you'll unlock new building packs, keeping the experience fresh and exciting. Watch your village grow as you fill out the map, advancing to larger and more complex maps as you complete each level. The dynamic weather and day-night cycle add an extra layer of immersion, making your village feel alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/48cf23bdd1ae6370c7f6a0bd0de66081.poster.avif?t=1774500989\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/48cf23bdd1ae6370c7f6a0bd0de66081.webm?t=1774500989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/48cf23bdd1ae6370c7f6a0bd0de66081.mp4?t=1774500989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To add a competitive edge, we’ve included an <strong>ONLINE LEADERBOARD</strong> where you can see how your scores stack up against other players or your friends. Plus, the game supports <strong>ACHIEVEMENTS</strong>, <strong>CROSS-PLATFORM CLOUD SAVE</strong>, <strong>GAMEPAD SUPPORT</strong>, and even <strong>runs smoothly on the Steam Deck</strong>. It’s not just a game—it’s a little haven of creativity and strategy you can take anywhere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/8db7d69baa2fd0f8de3a3bfc276546a2.poster.avif?t=1774500989\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/8db7d69baa2fd0f8de3a3bfc276546a2.webm?t=1774500989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/8db7d69baa2fd0f8de3a3bfc276546a2.mp4?t=1774500989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to embark on a relaxing journey of village building, where every decision shapes your own little world. I can't wait for you to experience the joy and tranquility this game offers. Happy building!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please remember, this is a small game and developed by a single person🙂</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/8c617c64e671c624784a6e344af485c1.poster.avif?t=1774500989\" width=800 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/8c617c64e671c624784a6e344af485c1.webm?t=1774500989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/8c617c64e671c624784a6e344af485c1.mp4?t=1774500989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Basically potato but nice to have..</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/1569e00c25b6f2b6d033800f0a07519f.poster.avif?t=1774500989\" width=800 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/1569e00c25b6f2b6d033800f0a07519f.webm?t=1774500989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/1569e00c25b6f2b6d033800f0a07519f.mp4?t=1774500989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to <strong>HEXAROMA</strong>, the charming world of our island village builder! Dive into a relaxing yet challenging experience where puzzle and strategy meet city building. Set across beautiful hexagonal maps, this game lets you craft quaint villages amidst varied landscapes like snowy tundras, scorching deserts, lush steppes, towering mountains, and dense forests. As my first game, I am incredibly excited to share this cozy adventure with you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/1d4ad0625104285b5e42ca52f5ee3c46.poster.avif?t=1774500989\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/1d4ad0625104285b5e42ca52f5ee3c46.webm?t=1774500989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/1d4ad0625104285b5e42ca52f5ee3c46.mp4?t=1774500989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Why should you play this game? </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you're looking for a soothing yet engaging pastime, this is the perfect game for you. It’s designed to be a chill and wholesome escape, allowing you to unwind as you create adorable island communities. Whether you're a seasoned gamer or just looking for a relaxing way to pass the time, the delightful atmosphere and simple mechanics make it easy to pick up and enjoy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/c68c4e58ed33649be325b32b76e917d7.poster.avif?t=1774500989\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/c68c4e58ed33649be325b32b76e917d7.webm?t=1774500989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/c68c4e58ed33649be325b32b76e917d7.mp4?t=1774500989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay is straightforward but rewarding. Place buildings strategically to maximize your score—some structures thrive when close to others, while some need space to flourish. With each milestone you reach on the progress bar, you'll unlock new building packs, keeping the experience fresh and exciting. Watch your village grow as you fill out the map, advancing to larger and more complex maps as you complete each level. The dynamic weather and day-night cycle add an extra layer of immersion, making your village feel alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/48cf23bdd1ae6370c7f6a0bd0de66081.poster.avif?t=1774500989\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/48cf23bdd1ae6370c7f6a0bd0de66081.webm?t=1774500989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/48cf23bdd1ae6370c7f6a0bd0de66081.mp4?t=1774500989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To add a competitive edge, we’ve included an <strong>ONLINE LEADERBOARD</strong> where you can see how your scores stack up against other players or your friends. Plus, the game supports <strong>ACHIEVEMENTS</strong>, <strong>CROSS-PLATFORM CLOUD SAVE</strong>, <strong>GAMEPAD SUPPORT</strong>, and even <strong>runs smoothly on the Steam Deck</strong>. It’s not just a game—it’s a little haven of creativity and strategy you can take anywhere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/8db7d69baa2fd0f8de3a3bfc276546a2.poster.avif?t=1774500989\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/8db7d69baa2fd0f8de3a3bfc276546a2.webm?t=1774500989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/8db7d69baa2fd0f8de3a3bfc276546a2.mp4?t=1774500989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to embark on a relaxing journey of village building, where every decision shapes your own little world. I can't wait for you to experience the joy and tranquility this game offers. Happy building!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please remember, this is a small game and developed by a single person🙂</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/8c617c64e671c624784a6e344af485c1.poster.avif?t=1774500989\" width=800 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/8c617c64e671c624784a6e344af485c1.webm?t=1774500989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056580/extras/8c617c64e671c624784a6e344af485c1.mp4?t=1774500989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Basically potato but nice to have..</p>",
